Paper calculates that Tetracycline was presented in therapeutic levels, not just trace amounts.

Tetracycline and similar drugs like Minocycline, Doxycycline have quinone properties, are able to oxidize lactic acid into Pyruvate and thus have anti-tumor effects, they work as Nitric Oxide inhibitors in brain and other tissues. Also shows we are too paranoid about antibiotics.
